      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Kieran Greer</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"http://www.qub.ac.uk/qc/webpages/whatwedo/researchgroups/environmentalmodelling/stafflist/qcindex.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/93/Kieran.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"312\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Kieran.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Kieran Greer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Kieran Greer</b>,<br />\na British computer scientist, researcher in <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a> and <a href=\"/Cognition\" title=\"Cognition\">cognition</a>, and programmer. He completed a DPhil in 1998 at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Ulster\">University of Ulster</a> at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jordanstown\">Jordanstown</a> with the thesis <i>A Neural Network Based Search Heuristic and its Application to Computer Chess</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . He introduced the related <a href=\"/Chessmaps_Heuristic\" title=\"Chessmaps Heuristic\">Chessmaps heuristic</a>, which is applied in his <a href=\"/ChessMaps\" title=\"ChessMaps\">ChessMaps</a> chess playing program, written in <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> . Kieran Greer holds a patent of a Chess variant with mined squares <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1997_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1997 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1997_...\">1997 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1997 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Piyush_Ojha&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Piyush Ojha (page does not exist)\">Piyush Ojha</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=David_A._Bell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"David A. Bell (page does not exist)\">David A. Bell</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i>Learning Search Heuristics from Examples: A Study in Computer Chess</i>. Seventh Conference of the Spanish Association for Artificial Intelligence, CAEPIA’97, November, pp. 695-704.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>A Neural Network Based Search Heuristic and its Application to Computer Chess</i>, D.Phil. Thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Ulster\">University of Ulster</a>.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Piyush_Ojha&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Piyush Ojha (page does not exist)\">Piyush Ojha</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=David_A._Bell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"David A. Bell (page does not exist)\">David A. Bell</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>A Pattern-Oriented Approach to Move Ordering: the Chessmaps Heuristic</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#22_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 22, No. 1</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Computer chess move-ordering schemes using move influence</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_%28journal%29\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 120, No. 2</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Thinking Networks - the Large and Small of it: Autonomic and Reasoning Processes for Information Networks</i>. ISBN: 9781440433276</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a>, Matthias Baumgarten, Maurice Mulvenna, Kevin Curran, Chris Nugent (<b>2008</b>). <i>Stigmergic Linking for Optimising and Reasoning Over Information Networks</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Ulster\">University of Ulster</a> Research Report, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/documents/ReasonLink.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Chess with Mined Squares</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/Documents/ChessMines.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.hindawi.com/journals/aai/2013/357068/\">Tree Pruning for New Search Techniques in Computer Games</a></i>. Advances in Artificial Intelligence, Vol. 2013</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Dynamic Move Chains – a Forward Pruning Approach to Tree Search in Computer Chess</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1403.0778\">arXiv:1403.0778</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Is Intelligence Artificial?</i> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1403.1076\">arXiv:1403.1076</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Turing: Then, Now and Still Key</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1403.2541\">arXiv:1403.2541</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Alan_Turing\" title=\"Alan Turing\">Alan Turing</a>, <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>New Ideas for Brain Modelling</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1403.1080\">arXiv:1403.1080</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>New Ideas for Brain Modelling 2</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1408.5490\">arXiv:1408.5490v2 </a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2015-2018</b>). <i>A More Human Way to Play Computer Chess</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1503.04333\">arXiv:1503.04333v4</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>New Ideas for Brain Modelling 3</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1612.00369\">arXiv:1612.00369</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>New Ideas for Brain Modelling 4</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1708.04806\">arXiv:1708.04806</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Memory, Search and Sense: A Theory about Nesting and Abstraction</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.01690\">\tarXiv:1803.01690</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.co.uk/citations?user=BYOADFgAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Kieran Greer - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.qub.ac.uk/qc/webpages/whatwedo/researchgroups/environmentalmodelling/stafflist/qcindex.html\">Staff and Students working in QEMG</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/index.html\">Distributed Computing Systems Home Page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/research.html\">Distributed Computing Systems - Research</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieran_Greer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.qub.ac.uk/qc/webpages/whatwedo/researchgroups/environmentalmodelling/stafflist/qcindex.html\">Staff and Students working in QEMG</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>A Neural Network Based Search Heuristic and its Application to Computer Chess</i>. D.Phil. Thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Ulster\">University of Ulster</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/chessmapsdownload.html\">ChessMaps Download</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieran Greer</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Chess with Mined Squares</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/Documents/ChessMines.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.distributedcomputingsystems.co.uk/publications.html\">Kieran Greer's Publications</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Greer:Kieran.html\">dblp: Kieran Greer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Alan_Turing\" title=\"Alan Turing\">Alan Turing</a> (<b>1950</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://loebner.net/Prizef/TuringArticle.html\">Computing Machinery and Intelligence</a></i>. Mind, 59, 433-460. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://archive.computerhistory.org/projects/chess/related_materials/text/2-0%20and%202-1.Computing_machinery_and_intelligence.turing/2-0%20and%202-1.Computing_machinery_and_intelligence.turing-alan.mind-59.1950.062303001.pdf\">pdf</a> from <a href=\"/The_Computer_History_Museum\" title=\"The Computer History Museum\">The Computer History Museum</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301012907\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 147/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 310/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTran